{"tid":625623,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"小心騙子! 分辨俄羅斯藍貓和英國短毛貓!","createTime":"2018-04-11T15:18:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-11T15:26:58.000Z","uid":181662,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"53e24f193d327349027f3a7d14b37c741918803a","tid":625623,"uid":181662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T15:18:50.000Z","msg":"首先聲明一下, 貓咪沒有貴賤之分, 純種貓和家貓都是平等的生命~<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但最近發現有人用英國短毛貓去扮俄羅斯藍貓騙人, 大家小心~<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1. 俄藍的眼球一定是綠色的, 可能會帶些少金; 而英短的眼就是黃色的.<br />\n2. 俄藍的面型是瘦長; 而英短就是圓面的.<br />\n3. 俄藍的身型比較幼長; 而英短就是比教粗大.<br />\n4. 價錢方面, 俄藍一般會比英短貴3000-8000港元不等.<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">俄羅斯藍貓</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/11/231730_e75b057036e94eb4f1cfdb97eff2d157.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F11%2F231730_e75b057036e94eb4f1cfdb97eff2d157.jpg&h=cb05d6d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><br />\n英國短毛貓</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/11/231738_3bc4331e47e694bd632c60fce656f65a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F11%2F231738_3bc4331e47e694bd632c60fce656f65a.jpg&h=9cedcb5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">騙子</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/11/231746_c8812facc7367186596b752f08b20454.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F11%2F231746_c8812facc7367186596b752f08b20454.jpg&h=c2e057aa&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8c55ec686076da9e551ecc2a2acfc18eff4f6a3e","tid":625623,"uid":62822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T15:26:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}